      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FRED'S FURY (7) was in winning form two back (22.60) at this track but ran below best last time at Geelong, finishing 7th. Strike rate this course and distance strong having won three of five tries. Won at his only start from this box. Looks the one to beat on his best form. BISMUTH (8) boxed on well to finish third last time, beaten one length (23.11) behind Paw Lara at Geelong. Expected to feature. MADDY GIBLET (1) is suited by the inside draw. Last start finished 4th in a Bottom Up - Grade 5 on May 18 over 390m at this track behind Aston Finniss beaten 9 lengths (22.82). Looks one of the chances. MORAINE MILEY (2) won as expected last time and is sure to feature again.",
